com.fchavez.jashinhurst.hw4.one

Class MIDI

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fchavez.jashinhurst.hw4.one.MIDI

  • public class MIDI
extends java.lang.Object

    This class holds information about a SPN note. It holds information such as the NoteValue and the MIDI number. The class will also handle the SPN form of the note and differing octaves.

    Version:
    hw1 #1
    Author:
    Franz Chavez, Joshua Ashinhurst
